OL,3,CFamily angry at lack of official event
OL,4,Cto mark 30 years since RAF Chinook
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FThe family of a man who was killed in
OL,8,Fan RAF Chinook helicopter crash have
OL,9,Fexpressed anger after they were told
OL,10,Fthe Ministry of Defence has not
OL,11,Farranged an official memorial to mark
OL,12,Fthe 30th anniversary of the incident.
OL,14,FTwenty-nine people were killed when
OL,15,Fthe helicopter carrying leading
OL,16,Fsecurity personnel crashed on the Mull
OL,17,Fof Kintyre peninsula on the west coast
OL,18,Fof Scotland on June 2, 1994.
