OL,7,FThe aircraft was on its way from RAF
OL,8,FAldergrove near Belfast to a security
OL,9,Fconference in Inverness when it
OL,10,Fcrashed into a hillside in thick fog.
OL,12,FThe incident was the worst RAF
OL,13,Fpeacetime disaster and the reasons for
OL,14,Fthe crash remain unclear.
OL,16,FThe pilots, flight lieutenants
OL,17,FJonathan Tapper and Richard Cook, were
OL,18,Finitially accused of gross negligence
OL,19,Fover the crash.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/9
