OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FBut a review of the incident in 2011
OL,8,Ffound the pilots should not have been
OL,9,Fblamed.
OL,11,FSusan Phoenix, whose husband Detective
OL,12,FSuperintendent Ian Phoenix of the
OL,13,FRoyal Ulster Constabulary was killed
OL,14,Fin the crash, has accused the Ministry
OL,15,Fof Defence (MoD) of a cover-up.
OL,17,FThe 75-year-old said she was appalled
OL,18,Fwhen she was told it had not organised
OL,19,Fan official commemoration to mark the
OL,20,F30th anniversary.
