OL,7,FDr Phoenix, who lives in Dorset, said:
OL,8,F"On the upcoming 30th anniversary of
OL,9,Fthis still-controversial, unresolved
OL,10,Fcrash that took the lives of 29 good
OL,11,Fpeople, including my husband, I am
OL,12,Ftold that there will be no official
OL,13,Fmemorial service ` just something 'low
OL,14,Fkey'.
OL,16,F"That is yet one more sign of a cover-
OL,17,Fup by the MoD ` a mission which began
OL,18,Fon June 2, 1994 when the Chinook
OL,19,Fcrashed and continues to this day.
