OL,7,F"They would prefer to sweep this all
OL,8,Funder the carpet, content in their
OL,9,Fivory towers waiting for all family
OL,10,Fmembers to die and fade away.
OL,12,F"It is a dereliction of the duty they
OL,13,Fowe to those who were killed, to the
OL,14,Fmemory of those they wrongly blamed,
OL,15,Fand to the families who still remain
OL,16,Fin limbo."
