OL,7,FA BBC documentary earlier this year
OL,8,Fraised further questions about the
OL,9,Fcrash, its aftermath and why no-one
OL,10,Fhas held to account for it, including
OL,11,Fthose who wrongly blamed the pilots.
OL,13,FDr Phoenix said: "Those of us who are
OL,14,Fnot dead will not stop asking
OL,15,Fquestions.
