OL,7,F"I refuse to wither on the vine for
OL,8,Fthe comfort of unconscionable
OL,9,Fofficials who let my husband and his
OL,10,Fcolleagues die in a non-airworthy
OL,11,Fcraft, then sought to assuage their
OL,12,Fguilt on two good men no longer alive
OL,13,Fto defend themselves."
OL,15,FHer son Niven, a former military and
OL,16,Fnow commercial pilot, hit out at the
OL,17,F"scapegoating of two young pilots who
OL,18,Fwere no longer able to defend
OL,19,Fthemselves in death".
