OL,7,FHe claimed the authorities "turned
OL,8,Ftheir backs on justice, even after the
OL,9,Ftruth was revealed" and that senior
OL,10,Fofficers and officials were never held
OL,11,Fto account.
OL,13,FThe independent review, announced in
OL,14,F2010 and published in 2011, found that
OL,15,Fcriticism of the Board of Inquiry on
OL,16,Fthe grounds that insufficient
OL,17,Fattention was paid to airworthiness
OL,18,Fand maintenance aspects was
OL,19,Funjustified.
