OL,7,FAn MoD spokesperson said: "The Mull of
OL,8,FKintyre was a tragic accident and our
OL,9,Fthoughts and sympathies remain with
OL,10,Fthe families, friends and colleagues
OL,11,Fof all those who died.
OL,13,F"In 2010, the Mull of Kintyre
OL,14,Findependent review was carried out and
OL,15,Fthe findings were fully accepted.
OL,17,F"The review did not find new evidence
OL,18,Fto suggest mechanical failure, and no
OL,19,Fsafety issues with the Chinook Mark 2
OL,20,Fwere raised in the report."
